      "markText": "王安石通过他的新政，努力为他理想化的国家最佳利益服务，有时，甚至以牺牲其社会出身所属的阶级（class）为代价。然而，他的许多追随者，相对于国家利益，更认同他们的阶级利益——如果不是个人利益的话。",
      "totalCount": 270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300011716&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6277&rangeEnd=6461",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c8b32a20813ab6b13g0169bd?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6277&rangeEnd=6461"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300011716_7_3512-3566",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3512-3566",
      "markText": "熙宁二年（1069）九月，推出农业贷款，即所谓“青苗钱”，提供给农民以用于播种，收获之后再连本带息一起偿还。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300011716&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3512&rangeEnd=3566",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c8b32a20813ab6b13g0169bd?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3512&rangeEnd=3566"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300011716_17_5021-5070",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "5021-5070",
      "markText": "王安石可能从未意识到，他的新政通过加强中央集权和要求他所认为的必要的同一性，会导致这样不幸的结局。",
      "totalCount": 198,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300011716&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=5021&rangeEnd=5070",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c8b32a20813ab6b13g0169bd?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=5021&rangeEnd=5070"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300011716_11_2377-2451",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "2377-2451",
      "markText": "王安石明确认为，相比于道德的自我养成（修己），即个人或内在的个体控制，【33】体制的或从外在对人们道德生活的控制即使不是更重要的话，也是更为有效的。",
      "totalCount": 187,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300011716&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2377&rangeEnd=2451",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c8b32a20813ab6b13g0169bd?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2377&rangeEnd=2451"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300011716_22_1712-1776",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "1712-1776",
      "markText": "人们不禁会问，这样一种道德主义的方法是否足够现实。它是否掩盖了一个官僚制国家的生活真相，从而抑制了后来的中国人思考政治体制问题？",
      "totalCount": 160,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300011716&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=1712&rangeEnd=1776",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c8b32a20813ab6b13g0169bd?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=1712&rangeEnd=1776"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300011716_3_672-709",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "672-709",
      "markText": "读其书而不知其人，则不能透彻体悟其书；论其人而不知其事，则不能真正理解其人",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300011716&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=672&rangeEnd=709",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c8b32a20813ab6b13g0169bd?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=672&rangeEnd=709"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300011716_10_5731-5825",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "5731-5825",
      "markText": "但是在反对新政和批评北方的保守主义的同时，温和派很少能提供具有建设性的备选方案，而倾向于吹毛求疵。既然这一学派在政治和学术上都是少数派，舞台中心则主要是围绕新学和北方保守主义者之间的冲突。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300011716&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5731&rangeEnd=5825",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c8b32a20813ab6b13g0169bd?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5731&rangeEnd=5825"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300011716_12_9488-9560",
